query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-xml',
'contact',
'core-plot',
'delimiter',
'delphi-xe2',
'difference',
'firebase-security-rules',
'jquery-datatables',
'sharepoint-online',
'shuffle',
'snmp',
'transparent',
'uialertview',
'vuetify.js',
'windows-ce');
